<A>__{zmuda gasps. two guards go running for him. zmuda barrels away, trying to escape. the guards chase. zmuda races by george, and suddenly palms off the camera into george's arms. the guards whip by, oblivious. george grimaces, unclear about his loyalties. he sweatily peers at the timebomb in his hands. and then george thrusts it under his jacket. he bolts for the door and feverishly scampers out.}
